{"tid":1525432,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"捉鬼一役差啲含家產！","createTime":"2019-09-01T00:12:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T00:15:47.000Z","uid":260414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9147f9ca3d00df65ef221c93664fad2cf6b4b1aa","tid":1525432,"uid":260414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T00:12:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">捉鬼依一下根本成個局咁！！！</span><br />\n<strong>琴晚成班跑走噴水池果邊想幫手，跑緊果陣我向後望果陣條街係仲有好多手足係到！</strong><br />\n<strong>之後最前噴水池班手足撤果陣！我地跑番轉頭，跑跑下我發現點解我面前係防暴！？</strong><br />\n<strong>我地20-30唯有跑入皇室堡，我自己一開頭跑錯路，一路係皇室堡停車場既對面，所有手足過哂去果陣我先發現我奶奶地野，我右邊不足10米係防暴，左邊就20米左右，而要過對面馬路就要跨欄，左右得番我一個，手足係哂對面，我果陣真係好驚，雖然最後我一氣呵成過到去。</strong><br />\n<strong>成件事好似引你去捉鬼，一捉後面就黎料，成個過程3分鐘都冇。</strong><br />\n<br />\n我知會有人話捉咩鬼，但捉到真係鬼果陣真係好難忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入到皇室堡我地諗住含家產，下面四面包圍，好彩保安最後都承諾左唔會放狗入場，唔係真係含家產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日去唔到機場啦，太攰，對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />各位手足加油"},{"pid":"388a81dd71973e9ae9eb3eac2f529b8e686e0ec5","tid":1525432,"uid":260414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T00:14:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港！時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"95de0c419a71bca5544969cccd05ba78cbb5dd2a","tid":1525432,"uid":287792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T00:15:47.000Z","msg":"誰能明白我 林子祥<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qdFoHjrXcHk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqdFoHjrXcHk&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b%2FY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=7d43af5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qdFoHjrXcHk</a>"}]}